<body>
    <h1>üì¶ Download Your Project</h1>
    <p>Click the button below to download all project files</p>
    
    <a href="/project-code.tar.gz" download class="download-btn">
        ‚¨áÔ∏è Download Project Files
    </a>

    <div class="steps">
        <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Extract the downloaded file</strong> (double-click on Mac)</li>
            <li><strong>Open Terminal</strong> and navigate to the folder:
                <br><code>cd ~/Downloads/app</code>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Make setup script executable:</strong>
                <br><code>chmod +x SETUP-GITHUB.sh</code>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Run the script:</strong>
                <br><code>./SETUP-GITHUB.sh</code>
            </li>
            <li><strong>Enter your GitHub token</strong> when prompted</li>
            <li><strong>Go to Cloudflare Dashboard</strong> and connect to GitHub</li>
        </ol>
    </div>
</body>
